luding one for  another  crap british horror comedy  i ve truly not seen the movie industry in a mess like this for a long timeexpect to see this movie for sale in the dvd bargain section for   in   months time  and if you re expecting to see a black comedy with tonnes of great looking snakes  and some bad ass cool dialogue coming from samuel l jacksons lips  forget it',-1

