ul he was  the lone bright spot here at all is seeing mr  sci fi himself  forrest j  ackerman  play the curator of a wax museum and chatting to his wax frankenstein affectionately called frankie  other than that this is a complete bust   now how is that for another tired  dreadful  trite pun',-1

